+----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${PKGSTEM} on OpenBSD
+----------------------------------------------------------------------

Playing idTech4A++ (Harmattan Edition) Engime games requires the Steam 
or GOG copy of the games. Copy all content of the original games to the 
appropriate directories:

~/.local/share/idtech4amm/doom3
~/.local/share/idtech4amm/quake4
~/.local/share/idtech4amm/prey

These direcotories will contain user data, such as game settings, 
log, and saves.

For more information, see:
https://github.com/glKarin/com.n0n3m4.diii4a
